My modification of the Rodinia GPU benchmark (CUDA ONLY) at
https://www.cs.virginia.edu/~skadron/lava/rodinia/downloads.html

1. Patch old code to new CUDA API
2. Bug fixes
3. Most importantly, experiment with various GPU optimization techniques on
these kernels.

Please note that the data is not uploaded with the repo. Please go to the
link above for the data.
